videos.description: Jalen Smith throws a cross-court pass to Eric Ayala who spots up to knock down a 3-pointer from the wing and extend Maryland's lead over Temple to 70-64.
videos.headline: Maryland's Ayala sinks big-time 3-pointer to pad Terps' lead
